{"tid":222532,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"劉德華今年係咪想洗底 《熱血合唱團》做指揮家","createTime":"2017-04-29T15:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T17:56:15.000Z","uid":76804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0a742628331b92be6673640089cc38935f74d5b","tid":222532,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T15:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5122A4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5122A4.jpg&h=e249fd3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《熱血合唱團》（Find Your Voice）是由關信輝執導、劉德華投資監製，劉德華、吳岱融、尹揚明、盧冠廷主演的一部香港青春勵志電影。預計2017年底在台灣上映。<br />\n<br />\n這是劉德華首次扮演一位音樂指揮家，為了演好角色，他在電影開拍前特意向音樂指揮家學習指揮技巧。<br />\n<br />\n五個小孩的校長導演 又係用小演員做主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e3f46320117b7fb5e5fa2a5101f5782f5f7926","tid":222532,"uid":10903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T17:56:15.000Z","msg":"今年佢好多戲上映，本來仲有演唱會。唉⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}